data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Don't wait 6 + months to build new when this is READY NOW. Home, Pool, and outdoor kitchen all completed THIS YEAR!! Still under warranty!!    This home features the "Modern Farmhouse" Design Collection interior: Sonoma Stone cabinets, Ethereal Wht Quartz counter-tops, Traveler 6”x24” Wht. wood tile flooring, and more. The Belmar impresses with its two-story volume ceiling in the foyer, which opens to the den, dining room and the split-garage entrances. The expansive combination island kitchen, grand room and cafe open to the oversized lanai for seamless indoor and outdoor living. Select from a downstairs guest suite, game room or owner’s retreat. Otherwise, upstairs is the unbelievable owner’s retreat complete with huge walk-in closet and generous bath. Secondary bedrooms joined with Jack and Jill bath, additional bed and bath, laundry, bonus room and incredible rear balcony round out the upstairs. Triple Creek is one of Riverview’s premier master planned communities with two separate clubhouses, multiple pools and one splash pad, tennis, basketball, walking and biking trails, playgrounds, fitness centers, meeting areas and more. Exterior Information: Pool and outdoor kitchen completed October 2023. Perfect place to call home!    This model is the only one on the market and won't last long! Take advantage of this WELL-PRICED gem! Don't wait, it'll be gone before you know it!!
